### Transaction endpoints — Makima API
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

@base_url = http://localhost:3000
@access_token = <access_token>
@portfolio_id = <portfolio_id>
@transaction_id = <transaction_id>
@asset_isin = IE00BK5BQT80

### List transactions in a portfolio
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/portfolios/{{portfolio_id}}/transactions?page=1&limit=25&transaction_type=Buy
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Create buy transaction
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/portfolios/{{portfolio_id}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "asset_isin": "{{asset_isin}}",
  "transaction_type": "Buy",
  "date": "2025-01-10",
  "settlement_date": "2025-01-12",
  "quantity": "10",
  "unit_price": "100",
  "commission": "1.50",
  "currency": "EUR",
  "notes": "Initial position"
}

###

### Create dividend transaction
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/portfolios/{{portfolio_id}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "asset_isin": "US0378331005",
  "transaction_type": "Dividend",
  "date": "2025-02-01",
  "gross_amount": "12.50",
  "tax_withheld": "2.50",
  "net_amount": "10.00",
  "currency": "USD"
}

###

### Get transaction by ID
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/transactions/{{transaction_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Update transaction
PUT {{base_url}}/api/v1/transactions/{{transaction_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "asset_isin": "{{asset_isin}}",
  "transaction_type": "Buy",
  "date": "2025-01-11",
  "quantity": "12",
  "unit_price": "101",
  "commission": "2.00",
  "currency": "EUR",
  "notes": "Adjusted quantity"
}

###

### Delete transaction
DELETE {{base_url}}/api/v1/transactions/{{transaction_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
